<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>MiCounselor Activation Email</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .email-header {
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #ec4899 100%);
        }

        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .email-header h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 32px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .activation-code {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .activation-code h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #7c3aed;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .timer {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .timer-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            fill: #6b7280;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .email-footer {
            padding: 24px 32px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .support-link {
            color: #7c3aed;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .support-link svg {
            margin-left: 4px;
        }

        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 24px;
            }

            .email-body {
                padding: 24px;
            }

            .activation-code h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Activate Your MiCounselor Account</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p class="welcome-text">Hello</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with MiCounselor! To ensure the security of your account, please verify your email address using the activation code below:</p>
            
            <div class="activation-code">
                <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
                <div class="timer">
                    <svg class="timer-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12,2A10,10 0 0,0 2,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,22A10,10 0 0,0 22,12A10,10 0 0,0 12,2M12,4A8,8 0 0,1 20,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,20A8,8 0 0,1 4,12A8,8 0 0,1 12,4M12.5,7H11V13L16.2,16.2L17,14.9L12.5,12.2V7Z" />
                    </svg>
                    Valid for 5 minutes
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Enter this code on the activation page to complete your registration and start your journey with MiCounselor.</p>
            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">If you didn't create a MiCounselor account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                Need help? Contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:support@micounselor.com" class="support-link">
                    support@micounselor.com
                    <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>